parameters:
"Makoto... where is this...? Why are we... in a place like
this...?"
"Heh heh, I had my underlings bring you here on my orders."
"You are... Suzuki!? What are you planning to do with us!?"

"Sure, I have a use for you too... but first, I'll start
with that bitch over there."

"Hey Asahi. You realize you're at my mercy, right? After all
this time, I haven't had a chance to fuck you."

"F-fuck!? What are you talking about! There's no way Makoto
would have sex with someone like you!"

"Hahahaha. Your childhood friend says otherwise, eh? Why
don't you tell him from your own mouth what happened,
Asahi?"

"Ma-Makoto... it's not true, right...? There's no way you'd
do something with this guy..."

"On the Friday after spring break... I was abducted by this
guy. And inside this factory... I was raped."

"That time was the best, wasn't it? Even though it was your
first time, you moaned like an idiot!!"

"That's because you drugged me! You made me do such...
disgusting things...!"

"And to top it off, you took photos and videos... and then
you started threatening me to serve you..."

"Exactly! I was supposed to make you serve me! But after
raping you, I couldn't fuck you at all!"

"Every time I called you out after that, something would
always happen by chance! Power outages, small fires... I
kept getting injured every time!"

"But it wasn't by chance, I finally realized... It was all
you, wasn't it? Right, Sato?!"

"Wh-what are you saying... Mamoru wouldn't do something like
that..."

"Before coming here, I heard from my underlings! You've been
seen around my house and the neighboring town!"

"Whether it's my house, the neighboring town, or the
factory!! You've been interfering with me, haven't you!!
Answer me!!"

"Ma-Mamoru... is it true...? It wasn't by chance... you did
all that...?"
"Yes... I was the one always interfering..."

"You admit it, you bastard...!! Because of you, I had to go
to the hospital so many times!!"

"I-I was just trying to help Makoto escape, I didn't
directly do anything to you!"

"Wait a minute! So Mamoru, you knew?! That I was being
blackmailed by Suzuki...?"

"No, I only found out about that just now. I thought you
were caught up in something bad, but..."

"But I never imagined you had been raped... I'm sorry,
Makoto... If I had been with you..."

"Don't apologize, Mamoru. It's my fault for carelessly going
home alone in the first place."

"And yet, you've saved me from Suzuki so many times... I
can't thank you enough..."
"Hey, stop blabbering!! I'm not done talking yet!!"

"I'm seriously pissed off that my plan was screwed up by
that damn glasses-wearing bastard...!!"

"That's right... Hey Asahi! Suck my dick right now!! I'll
show him how you get dirtied!!"

"Don't listen to Suzuki, Makoto! Suzuki! Don't you dare
touch Makoto anymore!"

"Stop, Mamoru... don't provoke him... I'll distract Suzuki,
so you take the chance to escape..."

"I can't do that!! I'd rather take a beating than let Makoto
be humiliated!!"

"Hey hey hey. Getting a little too cocky in front of your
childhood friend, aren't you? Should I have those thugs
break your bones again?"

"Please, stop Mamoru... why do you always try to save
me...?"
"...Huh?... Mamoru... did you just say you love me?"

"That's right! I love you! That's why I can't stand to see
you suffer!"

"Hey Suzuki! Call your goons! And beat me up as much as you
like! But in exchange, let Makoto go... just release her!"

"Hahahahaha!! You're getting pretty bold!! Who would go this
far for a second-hand woman?!"

"I don't care about that! So what if she was raped! That
doesn't change my feelings one bit!"

"No matter what happens, I love Makoto! I'd do anything to
protect her!"

"Whew! How cool! You're like a hero! But do you think I'd
take orders from you, idiot?"

"I'm talking to Asahi right now, not you. Hey Asahi, come
on! Suck my cock!"

"You're under my thumb! If you don't hurry up, I'll spread
your rape video all over the net..."

"Do as you like. If you want to release it on the net, then
go ahead."

"I didn't want only you to know that I was raped. I was
afraid of being hated because of my tainted body."

"But just now, you said it didn't matter. That you love me
no matter what..."

"Thanks to you, I've made up my mind too... I don't care how
the world sees me anymore."

"Mamoru... I love you too. As long as I have you, that's
enough. I don't care if the video gets exposed. I won't obey
him anymore."

"Hey, don't get all excited on your own!! Fine! I'll send
both of you to hell together!"
"Did you call for us, young master?"

"Yeah! First, break the glasses guy's limbs! After that,
we'll drug Asahi..."

"I'll show you, unable to move, how Asahi gets violated
right before your eyes! Hahahahahaha!!"
"Eh? Who... is that someone you know, Mamoru...?"

"You guys are... the ones who used to come to school every
morning to see Makoto..."
"What the hell are you guys!? Where did you pop out from!?"

"We are fans of Makoto-sama. We came all the way here after
learning she was taken away."

"Everything you've said here has been recorded! To think you
humiliated Makoto-sama and even threatened her...!"

"Your actions are unforgivable! You will receive the
appropriate retribution!"

"Fans of Asahi~? Hahahaha! Do fans really come all the way
to places like this!?"

"So what if three more female pigs showed up! As long as we
don't let them escape, it's fine to record the
conversation!"
"Hey you guys!! Start by hurting those idiots... what!? "

"What the... these guys appeared out of nowhere...! My
men... they were taken down in an instant...!"

"These kids... are too strong... damn it, to think I got
hired by such a brat... ugh..."

"This is what happens when you hire amateurs. If only you
hadn't been stingy and hired professionals instead."

"They are our bodyguards, the three sisters. Our father
provided us with the best of the best."

"Now, there's no one left to help you. Surrender quietly. If
you do, we'll spare your life."

"...Don't mess with me. Don't mess with me, don't mess with
me, don't mess with meeeee!!"

"Why does everything always get in my wayyyyy!! Why can't
things go my wayyyyy!!"

"Damn it, damn it, damn it, damn it, damn itttt!! At
least... Asahi... you alone!!"

"I'm a ranked martial artist! I won't be outdone by someone
like you! Yaaaaaaaah!!"

"Oh... as expected of Makoto... there was no problem at
all..."

"Ah... doing something like this in front of Mamoru... Well,
Mamoru? Do you... dislike strong women...?"

"Of course not! You were so cool! I've fallen for you all
over again! You're the best, Makoto!"

"C-cool... Uuu... I wanted you to think of me as a cute
girl..."

"Flirting with Makoto-sama right in front of us...! Shall we
erase this glasses-wearing guy...!"

"Please, refrain. He is a wonderful gentleman who cares
about Makoto-sama more than anyone else."

"It's frustrating, but the two of them make a perfect
couple... Makoto-sama also seems happy, so with this, the
matter is settled!"

Afterward, the police arrived and took Suzuki and his men
away. Triggered by the video recorded by the three sisters,
a house search was conducted, and a large amount of drugs
were found at Suzuki's home, leading to his arrest without
fail.

Furthermore, due to the scandal caused by his son, the stock
prices of Suzuki's father's company plummeted. Additionally,
employees who had been harboring grievances began to blow
the whistle one after another, exposing all the misdeeds the
Suzuki family had committed.

The Suzuki company went bankrupt, and Suzuki's father seemed
to have vanished like smoke. Rumor has it, he was taken away
by men with scary faces. Most likely, he received some form
of retribution from dangerous people.

In any case, with this, the incident was brought to a close
for the time being. After the event, I went home with
Makoto, and her parents, upon receiving the news, cried
tears of joy for their daughter's return.

Makoto confessed everything to her parents about being
blackmailed by Suzuki. Although her parents were deeply
saddened to learn their daughter had been raped, Makoto held
my hand tightly and said with a smile that she didn't mind
any retaliation.

But there stood the head of the mighty Asahi conglomerate.
That wasn't enough, and after making a phone call somewhere,
they immediately began to deal with the video in question.

They thoroughly investigated Suzuki's home before the house
search and destroyed all media containing the video,
including backups on the internet, in the blink of an eye.

Indeed, the power of the conglomerate was not to be
underestimated. Even Makoto didn't expect the video to be
completely erased, and when she received the report, she
laughed with a mix of joy and amazement.

And since it was a good opportunity, she also conveyed that
she was dating me. Makoto's parents gladly accepted our
relationship, saying they could trust their daughter with
someone who had protected her.

Thus, we officially became a couple with the blessing of our
parents. Being able to date my beloved Makoto feels like a
dream. But the changes that happened around me didn't stop
there.
